drm: Cancel drm_fb_helper_resume_work on unload

We can not allow the worker to run after its fbdev, or even the module,
has been removed.

Fixes: cfe63423d9be ("drm/fb-helper: Add drm_fb_helper_set_suspend_unlocked()")
